<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pass-away">pass away</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[委婉语] 去世；逝世：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sadly, my grandmother passed away two years ago but I still think of her all the time.
不幸的是，我的祖母两年前去世了，但我还是一直想起她。</p><footer>北师大新选必① – 1改</footer></div></div>